<p>Make a call to action and ask your user to share. This is the second message your audience will see on your button after an emoji is clicked on. This message will trigger the popup overlay for your users to share and further engage with your page.</p><p>Be creative and give your user a reason to click to share. If left blank, our factory message will be displayed "Share Now"</p><p><strong>Important note:</strong> If you disable social sharing this feature will be deactivated and only the first call to action message will be shown for user engagement.</p><p><i>Use the preview to see how it works.</i></p>